    "Bob": 6.5,
    "Dan": 2.75
  },
  "balance": 12.75
}
```

I'll need to carefully manage the debt calculations. The balance is computed by summing all amounts 
owed to the user and subtracting all amounts the user owes. This requires tracking both directions of 
debt precisely.

